      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "DIM SIM OLLIE (7) finds it hard to win. Finished third (22.74) at this track latest and might be close to finding winning form again. Solid formlines coming through his last run. One of the contenders. WE ARE SOUTH (5) hit the ground running from an outside draw with a fast early split, holding on for a minor placing when second and beaten half a length at this track over 390m in 22.76. Ready to find winning form. HILLBILLY ROCKY (1) had a low draw last time over 425m at Bendigo but was in traffic and failed to finish. Returns here after a three-and-a-half months spell. May be worth another try here fresh. OUR BOY BILLY (2) can feature with the right run.",
